725039f-a.title: Queens: 14th Road - 150th Place
725039f-a.text:
14th Road, at the S.W. corner of 150th Place, viewing
eastward and showing an old home. It does not, however,
appear in Wolvertonte 1891 atlas.
P. L. Sperr  March 5, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725040f-a.title: Queens: 14th Road - 150th Place
725040f-a.text:
14th Road, north side, between 150th Place and Cross Island
Boulevard. This house was owned by J. Eennedy in 1873. 14th
Road was then known as 17th Street.
P. L. Sperr  March 5, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
